Package: com.samuel2672.python3-rootless
Name: Python 3.12 Rootless
Version: ${PY_VER}-1
Section: Development
Priority: optional
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Maintainer: samuel2672
Installed-Size: ${INSTALLED_SIZE}
Depends: firmware (>= 14.5)
Icon: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/samuel2672/python3.12-ios-arm64-rootless/refs/heads/main/icons/icon.png
Description: Python 3.12 interpreter for rootless iOS jailbreaks.
 This package provides a Python 3.12 environment installed under /var/jb/usr/local.
 .
 Included:
  * Python 3.12 interpreter
  * Standard library with SSL support
  * ctypes FFI support
  * native subprocess experiment support
  * zlib, bz2 and lzma compression support
 .
 Note: pip is not installed by default. To install it, run:
  python3.12 -m ensurepip --upgrade
